BEYOND the DARKNESS in Memoriam Episode: Lorraine Warren the First Lady of the Paranormal.
Listen Here

Through our 13 years we were lucky enough to have spoken to Lorraine Warren a handful of times, this was her final visit with us in conjunction with the release of The Conjuring.

Please enjoy her Final Appearance on our program.
